				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/D%E1%BA%A1-%E1%BA%A9m-thi/poem-iJf_3vecmrb3XeLiZCsmUg">Dạ ẩm thi - 夜飲詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/author-t4xvjEQCpJQuGs7GtUeU9A">Nguyễn Cư Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/%C4%90i%E1%BB%83m-gi%C3%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-vqAuPOZlFxK_e0SMBU4PIQ">Điểm giáng thần - Nguyệt dạ - 點絳唇－月夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-VcJOg6OMnUKwRFzXmhMIag">Triệu Trường Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-K%E1%BB%B7-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-luy%E1%BA%BFn-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-yvBz7Usb8BeAV-244A91gA">Điệp luyến hoa kỳ 2 - 蝶戀花其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-K%E1%BB%B7-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-P5gHWt0svykQZv94RUMFeg">Án Kỷ Đạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Lam-Anh/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/poem-ZqbcTmDc41U_zCxOSmhFjw">Khuất Nguyên - 屈原</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Lam-Anh/author-wuJAXMNBIWrb0vxwglcnTQ">Phạm Lam Anh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/K%C3%BD-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-c%E1%BB%91-h%E1%BB%AFu-h%E1%BB%93i-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-D1CmpdjouXtDoqvI_2hCyg">Ký Nguyễn cố hữu hồi tịch - 寄阮故友回藉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/L%C3%A3o-th%C3%A1i/poem-tvyfaC5bVR1EYeVmjs8jqA">Lão thái - 老態</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/L%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-qMR1OQDdKVeGZX82ZHVIwA">Lục thập tự thuật - 六述十自</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-YRtbQ4Y_EBSiaNimbo26Cg">Lê Khắc Cẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Th%C3%B4n-gia-th%C3%BA/poem-HSdmfXvnWf03rVguKNuJqg">Thôn gia thú - 村家趣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ti%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-1QyYtj392U9KThUlfaehoA">Thương tiến tửu - 將進酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/T%E1%BB%91ng-Trang-Xung-H%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%A9-Vi%E1%BB%87t/poem-SqnQBnzAIc-tyH8W1QcCCg">Tống Trang Xung Hư sứ Việt - 送莊沖虗使粵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-ZqGaWwKOrJXGaqhA3jlDaw">Viên Hoằng Đạo</a>)<br></div>	</div>
